  "body": "If you really want to upgrade your Migrations contract later, you'll have to do this instead. The reason is because it uses msg.sender and not tx.origin:\n\nvar old_migrations = Migrations.deployed();\ndeployer.deploy(Migrations).then(function() {\n  return old_migrations.last_completed_migrations.call();\n}).then(function(last_migration) {\n  var new_migrations = Migrations.deployed();\n  return new_migrations.setCompleted(last_migration);\n});\n",
